    <Text ID="1804771" Value="Waiting for falling edge of photo cell S4. Check lens for dirt or moisture. Adjust warning delay if required."/>
    <Text ID="1804772" Value="If datum gate moved, check position of reed switch. If datum gate did not move, check solenoid override switch. Check Air Pressure."/>
    <Text ID="1804773" Value="Waiting for rising edge of photo cell S6. Check lens for dirt or moisture. Adjust warning delay if required."/>
